tva:Review.tva:FreeTextReview: 100% agree dude, I love﻿ this new sound on the album and I love their old stuff too. I hate when people argue between new and old Green Day.

How is a band going to survive if they don't change with the times? If a band doesn't change with time, no one will follow them any more. I've bought every single CD by Green Day, Jjust because I like their old stuff, doesn't mean that I hate their new stuff. Become a bit﻿ more open minded before you post something. Anyways, who cares if know everything about Green Day. It's about the music, not the facts. Stop being a stereotypical, uncultured, close minded swine. It'd be much appreciated.

Yeah dude, I can listen to paper lanterns or private ale all day but I like these new songs too. And please stop with the "old﻿ green day is better" and "I know everything about green day", you just sound like a stupid 14 year old kid, just shut up.
If no one here appreciates this song they﻿ obviously aren't fans of The Clash either. This sounds just like one of their songs.
All you guys complaining about Oh Love's video; I heard they filmed these back to back. They wer obviously really excited for this one :3 it looks﻿ tight.
september... t4th﻿ september...
Damn﻿ i cant wait , i want the album NOW!
HOLY FUCK I cant wait﻿
We have 26 DJ's among us, you know , we have to do what BJ told us. HOLD HIM UNDER WATER TIL' THE﻿ MOTHERFUCKER DROWNS!
This reminds me of my psycho sweet﻿ 16
If no one appreciates this song then you're obviously﻿ not fans of The Clash. This sounds just like one of their songs.
How﻿ many times can someone say (sing) "fuck" and derivations in a radio/tv single? Billie Joe would say 18. I counted...
CAN'T﻿ WAIT!!!!! AAAAAAAH!
th﻿
It still just says the video? ﻿
The﻿ album is gonna be awesome.
Oh woops, i guess i don't know then, lol,﻿ maybe it come out the same time. If not, you could look it up.

It doesn't matter what era someone began to listen to Green Day, it's whether they enjoy the music that counts. But yeah, you have a point that their sound has massively changed and that's because as a band they have changed. You have a bad attitude about the﻿ fans. I was only about 10 when American Idiot came out, they formed many years before I was even born. So before you should stop judging people as fans based on what era got them into their music.

Really﻿ nice!
KILL THAT FCKING DJ﻿
